title: BumpSequenceResultCode
description:
BumpSequenceResultCode is an XDR Enum defines as:

```text enum BumpSequenceResultCode { // codes considered as "success" for the operation BUMP_SEQUENCE_SUCCESS = 0, // codes considered as "failure" for the operation BUMP_SEQUENCE_BAD_SEQ = -1 // `bumpTo` is not within bounds }; ```
